data.description: Move in ready beautifully remodeled home.  New kitchen with gas stove, vent range hood, all kitchen appliances stay. Very open main floor overlooks the back yard through a wall of windows. 3 good sized bedrooms on the 2nd floor. Basement has 4th bedroom, office, family room and laundry room includes the washer and dryer.  Backyard is fenced and includes a deck and patio along with a swing set. Oversized 2 stall tandem garage with over 600 square feet.
